description:
In this karaoke tribute to the great Jehovah, you'll enjoy gospel hymns and worship music performed by a full choir. This instrumental karaoke track is perfect for church services, holidays, or any other special occasion!

If you're looking for a fun and cathartic way to celebrate Jesus Christ, then this gospel karaoke track is perfect for you! Featuring beautiful hymns and worship music, this instrumental track will put you in the mood to worship and sing!

First Line : Guide me, O Thou great Jehovah
Title : Guide Me
Author : William Williams (1745)

Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters Youtube channel
